ch indie band Phoenix kick-started the final portion of the show with an electrifying set, before American singer H.E.R took the stage.\", \"from\": 4198, \"to\": 4337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4198, \"end\": 4204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9927349021205877, \"rank\": 0.004266418418197867, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 4300, \"end\": 4308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999996603037, \"rank\": 3.35752316461517e-10, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The night closed with Mission Impossible star Tom Cruise abseiling from the top of the stadium roofto take the Olympic flag for the next host Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 4339, \"to\": 4493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4361, \"end\": 4379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dave_Grohl\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.168559859317947e-36, \"text\": \"Mission Impossible\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dave_Grohl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dave_Grohl\"}, {\"begin\": 4385, \"end\": 4395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}, {\"begin\": 4481, \"end\": 4492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7193357689526026e-18, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\